user
can
run
this
program
either
interactively
or
non-
interactively.
The
program
will
be
run
non-
interactively
if
the
user
specifies
program
arguments
and
flag
settings
on
the
command
line
using
the
form:
     r.sun
     [-
     s]
     elevin
     =
     name
